\begin_layout Standard
There a three main tissue responses to neoplasia:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Desmoplasia: A stromal response as a reactive formation of connective tissue
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Inflammatory response: inflammatory cells rush in.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Vasucular: angiogenis of new blood cells - hard to tell in slide
\end_layout

